WEBVTT - Close Eye Founder Story

scene-0-line-0
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.930
Hi. I'm Krishna.

scene-0-line-1
00:00:01.980 --> 00:00:03.190
Not the Founder.

scene-0-line-2
00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:03.890
Not the CEO.

scene-0-line-3
00:00:03.940 --> 00:00:05.150
Just Krishna.

scene-1-line-0
00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:07.910
Thank you for taking a few minutes to listen.

scene-1-line-1
00:00:07.960 --> 00:00:09.370
Before I tell you about Close Eye,

scene-1-line-2
00:00:09.420 --> 00:00:12.650
I want to tell you about one day that changed my life.

scene-2-line-0
00:00:12.700 --> 00:00:14.750
A little while ago, on the 16th of June,

scene-2-line-1
00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:16.710
my daughter was born.

scene-2-line-2
00:00:16.760 --> 00:00:18.850
It was the happiest day of my life.

scene-2-line-3
00:00:18.900 --> 00:00:21.690
But somehow, it was also one of the loneliest.

scene-3-line-0
00:00:21.740 --> 00:00:24.350
In that room, there were only a few of us.

scene-3-line-1
00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:27.250
My wife. Our new baby.

scene-3-line-2
00:00:27.300 --> 00:00:31.030
My sister-in-law, who stayed with us the whole time.

scene-3-line-3
00:00:31.080 --> 00:00:33.270
And my parents.

scene-3-line-4
00:00:33.320 --> 00:00:35.870
Everyone else I loved was far away.

scene-4-line-0
00:00:35.920 --> 00:00:37.990
There was no crowd outside the door.

scene-4-line-1
00:00:38.040 --> 00:00:40.290
No phone ringing again and again.

scene-4-line-2
00:00:40.340 --> 00:00:42.710
For a few minutes, everything was quiet.

scene-4-line-3
00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:44.750
I held my daughter for the first time.

scene-4-line-4
00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:46.690
I wanted to tell the whole world.

scene-4-line-5
00:00:46.740 --> 00:00:50.190
But I realised — I had almost no one to call.

scene-5-line-0
00:00:50.240 --> 00:00:52.530
Then one thought came to my mind.

scene-5-line-1
00:00:52.580 --> 00:00:55.370
The same thought every parent has:

scene-5-line-2
00:00:55.420 --> 00:00:58.070
“What will happen to her if something happens to me?”

scene-5-line-3
00:00:58.120 --> 00:01:00.670
I didn't want someone to replace her family.

scene-5-line-4
00:01:00.720 --> 00:01:03.730
I wanted something that could make her family stronger.

scene-5-line-5
00:01:03.780 --> 00:01:06.790
Someone she can trust — when we can't be there.

scene-6-line-0
00:01:06.840 --> 00:01:08.290
Then I understood something.

scene-6-line-1
00:01:08.340 --> 00:01:10.730
Millions of families feel this same way.

scene-6-line-2
00:01:10.780 --> 00:01:12.150
Parents getting older.

scene-6-line-3
00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:15.410
Children living far away, in other countries.

scene-6-line-4
00:01:15.460 --> 00:01:17.670
Grandparents missing birthdays.

scene-6-line-5
00:01:17.720 --> 00:01:20.950
Every night, someone is thinking: “Are they okay?”

scene-7-line-0
00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.630
That was the moment Close Eye became real for me.

scene-7-line-1
00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:25.550
It was no longer just an idea.

scene-7-line-2
00:01:25.600 --> 00:01:26.910
It became my responsibility.

scene-7-line-3
00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:31.710
So that no family has to face life's big moments alone.

scene-8-line-0
00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:33.270
We don't replace families. We make them stronger.

scene-8-line-1
00:01:33.320 --> 00:01:36.670
We don't replace sons and daughters.

scene-8-line-2
00:01:36.720 --> 00:01:40.050
We help them stay close, even from far away.

scene-8-line-3
00:01:40.100 --> 00:01:41.790
We help families care for each other —

scene-8-line-4
00:01:41.840 --> 00:01:44.350
with love, respect, and trust.

scene-9-line-0
00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:46.450
Every visit. Every message.

scene-9-line-1
00:01:46.500 --> 00:01:48.190
Every companion. Every call.

scene-9-line-2
00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:49.590
Is a family trusting us.

scene-9-line-3
00:01:49.640 --> 00:01:51.410
When you join Close Eye,

scene-9-line-4
00:01:51.460 --> 00:01:53.610
you are not just joining a company.

scene-9-line-5
00:01:53.660 --> 00:01:56.610
You are becoming someone's trusted presence.

scene-10-line-0
00:01:56.660 --> 00:01:57.590
That day, I made one more promise.

scene-10-line-1
00:01:57.640 --> 00:02:01.770
Close Eye should not grow only for its founders.

scene-10-line-2
00:02:01.820 --> 00:02:04.130
It should grow with the people who build it.

scene-10-line-3
00:02:04.180 --> 00:02:07.630
Work like an owner. Be honest. Protect trust.

scene-10-line-4
00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:10.410
Because trust is not built by software.

scene-10-line-5
00:02:10.460 --> 00:02:12.230
Trust is built by people.

scene-11-line-0
00:02:12.280 --> 00:02:14.010
Every year, on the 16th of June,

scene-11-line-1
00:02:14.060 --> 00:02:15.270
we will celebrate Family Day.

scene-11-line-2
00:02:15.320 --> 00:02:18.730
To remember why Close Eye exists —

scene-11-line-3
00:02:18.780 --> 00:02:20.450
that every request is a real family,

scene-11-line-4
00:02:20.500 --> 00:02:25.030
and that no app can replace a real person being there.

scene-12-line-0
00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:26.670
One day, I hope you will meet my daughter.

scene-12-line-1
00:02:26.720 --> 00:02:28.130
Not because she is our brand.

scene-12-line-2
00:02:28.180 --> 00:02:32.470
But because she reminds us why this work matters.

scene-12-line-3
00:02:32.520 --> 00:02:34.950
Every child deserves grandparents.

scene-12-line-4
00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:38.510
Every grandparent deserves a child's laughter.

scene-12-line-5
00:02:38.560 --> 00:02:40.610
And every family deserves to stay close,

scene-12-line-6
00:02:40.660 --> 00:02:43.550
however far apart they live.

scene-13-line-0
00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:45.010
Please remember one thing.

scene-13-line-1
00:02:45.060 --> 00:02:46.810
Every notification. Every call.

scene-13-line-2
00:02:46.860 --> 00:02:48.330
Every visit. Every decision.

scene-13-line-3
00:02:48.380 --> 00:02:51.310
Is about someone's family.

scene-13-line-4
00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:53.930
Because of your work, someone will sleep peacefully tonight.

scene-13-line-5
00:02:53.980 --> 00:02:55.790
This is our responsibility.

scene-13-line-6
00:02:55.840 --> 00:02:57.290
This is our honour.

scene-13-line-7
00:02:57.340 --> 00:02:58.870
Welcome to Close Eye.

scene-13-line-8
00:02:58.920 --> 00:03:00.990
Thank you for believing in this mission.

scene-13-line-9
00:03:01.040 --> 00:03:03.310
Thank you for becoming part of Close Eye.

scene-13-line-10
00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:06.380
Together, let's build the world's most trusted presence network.
